---
description: Global router for this repository. Maps user intent to canonical skills in .claude/skills.
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Use `.claude/skills` as canonical source.

Routing priority:
1. Planning intent -> `task-planner`
2. Debug intent -> `debug-strategist`
3. Lint or format intent -> `lint-fix`
4. Final verification -> `format-lint-audit`

Never duplicate SKILL body here.
